{
  "stem": "13251.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He said, it wasn't your fault.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, it was scary.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, distant.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was uncomfortable in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And oh, another thing-- I was never that good in school because I had other-- my brother was great.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was well, maybe in the top third, but I was never-- didn't stand out because I never really gave it a full effort.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because I always put most of my energy in sport and art.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Those were my two subjects I was really good in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And all the subjects I had to do, you know, so I didn't really put a full effort.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But in this school, the teacher had like a couple of pets that were top in the class and all that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I ended up, I was not only first in the exam-- never in my life, in any school, was I top, number one-- I was not first in the exam.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they also do an overall term's work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was top in term-- you know, overall term's work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I overheard the teacher take these two guys and give them a lecture.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "How could you let this guy go ahead of you, and all that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You know, he's new here and everything else.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "See, I remember that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It's not that I'm that-- I was never that good of a student, but I think I was kind of driven to make an extra effort because of my situation, because normally I just didn't give it that much effort.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There's one guy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was like my idol, because he was older and I thought he was just a nice guy.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "His name is Benno Katz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He lives in, in West LA somewhere.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I kept in touch with him in Israel, because he went to Israel.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there's one, Steiner.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
